{"tid":1902114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哇我屌你老母好多打手吹風投白票 + 簡單解釋佢哋嘅大話","createTime":"2020-02-28T07:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T06:53:04.000Z","uid":335921,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6117265d5f80fa6bce8d5b71652cacee22966ff0","tid":1902114,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"一打開連登，全登都有post屌泛民投票<br />\n明顯到咁連登仔唔會信掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單化解迷思:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">泛民連拉布都拉唔到投黎做咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n早前議會係共派嘅推動下改咗議事規則，基本上已經冇拉布依支歌仔唱。<br />\n<br />\n同時議會係玩半數制，即係多過一半人支持就可以通過議案，泛民目前係唔夠過半議席。你想屌泛民嘅不如摑自己兩巴點解以前唔投票咁不孝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你投票即係認可個制度，即係贊成勇武係暴徒。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先講得出依句嘅一係個腦有問題唔識政治，一係存心帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n參與選舉行使投票權係一個選民嘅基本權力同責任，我地做嘅係用投票去支持一種政治立場，而唔係我投票就等如支持政府。<br />\n<br />\n參與制度 不等如 認可制度<br />\n<br />\n你返學都唔代表你鐘意學校啦？<br />\n<br />\n係基於最大利益嘅情況下 (泛民過半數，重奪議會控制權)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">投票點都係最好方法，你要好有風骨咁唔投票做烈士係你嘅事，我地要嘅係民主，因此投票係唔應該放棄嘅戰線。</span><br />\n<br />\n要記住，理念上兄弟爬山，手足覺得有用嘅就由佢去做，做多樣好過做少樣。<br />\n<br />\n現實上制度抗爭同法外抗爭冇任何衝突，我地由此至於都係一群有共同目標同利益嘅手足，唔係單一個人，路線上有分歧有玩法正常不過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973268eea285cf251f668947d052e7fd8c00c913","tid":1902114,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"消息？睇真啲 切勿盡信"},{"pid":"3305889de869f91ed731f297e6f70cc0af4f00e8","tid":1902114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aca4bf7b2235a0996cffa46c16e9cb7c84050b","tid":1902114,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac05f4a322bf802eab25e11ab082c63e2f32c56","tid":1902114,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"建制一定要輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4837ed814017ee3042fdbb512f04a192c4c533cd","tid":1902114,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"[歷史假想] 如果當年台灣一早有熱狗日日叫人投白票的話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1899970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1899970</a>"},{"pid":"8b2fd40a001c493d5eee775048ef9ee2871cea20","tid":1902114,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"555f05a42928b333d791df3bfaf6480224b131d2","tid":1902114,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"諗起白兵，上次區選輸左，依加要出全力要你輸9月立法會選舉"},{"pid":"e83293b77822a399bceb37a3d838d272631b2df7","tid":1902114,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"班五毛扮自己友 含淚含撚含家產咩都出埋來 叫人投白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母以為咁就帶到風 實在太了解連登仔啦"},{"pid":"16a91dc5276d423e68599c90caa51d9b1885a92e","tid":1902114,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e83293b77822a399bceb37a3d838d272631b2df7","tid":1902114,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"班五毛扮自己友 含淚含撚含家產咩都出埋來 叫人投白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母以為咁就帶到風 實在太了解連登仔啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"上年區議會同一技倆"},{"pid":"02dc1798d3384eb8e3651dfba4632f857326adf1","tid":1902114,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555f05a42928b333d791df3bfaf6480224b131d2","tid":1902114,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0